    <!-- The Modal Background-->
    <div id="modalBG" class="modal-bg">

    <!-- Gopher It Modal content -->
        <div class="modal-content first-modal">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <div class="title"><h4>Why Gopher It</h4></div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>
                What is and why should you Gopher? Gopher help take the guess work out of trying find something to do.
                This site helps you and friends make plans easier and find fun events all can agree on.
                Why Gopher? Why not? Put in your state and pick an event you are in the mood for and let us do the rest.
                All that's left is you to pick what catches your eye, Boom you have your day planned.
                There is a  Feeling Lucky option for those adventurous types. 
                </p>
            </div>
            <span id="modalClose" class="modal-close">X</span>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!--Connect Modal Content-->
    <div id="connectModalBG" class="modal-bg">
        <div class="modal-content">
